language if he does not know it.  If the Adept puzzles out or knows
the language (from clues such as root words in known languages), he
will have rank with the language equal to half his Rank with this
talent (round up) after spending 20 hours (-30 minutes / Rank with this
talent) mastering the nuances of the language. A dead language may be
