according to  the  following  table:

{\setlength\leftmargini{0.5em}
\begin{description}
\setlength\itemsep{0pt}
\item[0] Full-sized (within  Rank  limits)  but  partially  incomplete  (GM's discretion).
\item[1]   Will  visually  appear  complete.
\item[3]   May add olfactory component.
\item[5]   May add auditory component.
\item[7]   May add tactile component.
\end{description}}
At Ranks 0--3 only a 1 hex sized illusion may be created.  For every
three Ranks after rank 3 or fraction thereof, another hex for the
purpose of size may be added.  For example, at rank 7 an illusion of a
three hex giant may be created.
