spells at any time that he is holding the Runewand while making a Cast
Check.  A character may add Fatigue to a Runewand any number of times,
so long as the Runewand has the capacity remaining to store the
Fatigue each time the wand is ``recharged''.  The Experience Multiple
for this ritual is 300.
