least once in the past.  He is present in that location in all ways
except bodily (ie.  he may communicate and use all his senses while
his image is there, but may not be harmed by any attack). The image
``mimics'' the actual actions of the Adept, and may move no more than
10 feet (+ 10 / rank) from the spot where it materialised, which may
be anywhere at the location the Adept wishes. Since the Adept's
consciousness is in the image, which is non-physical, he may not cast
any spells (although he may appear to should he so desire).
