a969 11
\emph{Effects: }
The Adept must, at the moment he casts the spell, touch the target he
intends to smite with the Runewand. If the target fails to
successfully resist, he suffers [D + 1] + 1 / Rank damage.  The target
takes half damage if fails to resist.  The damage is similar to the
effect of an electric shock, so halve the damage if the target is an
insulator (entities are generally not insulators). The touch is
automatic unless the target is actively avoiding being touched, in
which case the target cannot be touched and the spell cannot take
effect.  The spell must be prepared normally. If the target fails to
resist then they become stunned.
